You're right. I'm-I'm just...
I'm, you know...

33:10.514 --> 33:11.590
You're what?

33:14.523 --> 33:15.933
You're what, Kevin?

33:17.831 --> 33:20.633
You've been weird ever since
you got back to New York.

33:20.658 --> 33:21.980
- Have I? Okay.
- Yeah.

33:22.005 --> 33:25.097
You know, I-I never should have agreed

33:25.122 --> 33:26.847
to come here tonight, okay?

33:26.872 --> 33:29.394
I didn't want to let you down,
that's the truth, but I am...

33:31.943 --> 33:33.832
