33:37.283 --> 33:39.558
Now, look, I-I'm gonna...
I-I got to get...

33:40.638 --> 33:43.379
I probably just need some air,
so I'm gonna go, you know...

33:45.149 --> 33:46.996
I'll meet you back at your place, okay?

34:09.342 --> 34:11.621
You gonna stand out there forever?

34:13.650 --> 34:14.650
Yep.

34:17.395 --> 34:19.318
You can't grab me like that.

34:26.458 --> 34:29.052
The second-to-last home was the worst.

34:30.429 --> 34:33.091
I was always in trouble there.
We all were.

34:38.143 --> 34:40.474
It was because of the magazines.

34:42.902 --> 34:45.333
Foster mom, Alice,

34:46.263 --> 34:50.232
she had these subscriptions
to all the beauty magazines...

34:51.292 --> 34:53.989
<i>Glamour, Vogue, Cosmo.</i>

34:56.264 --> 34:59.021
I think her boyfriend knew
that we thought it was funny,

34:59.984 --> 35:01.652
'cause she was ugly.

35:04.717 --> 35:06.560
She was butt-ugly.

35:09.474 --> 35:11.669
That's why he used them on us.

35:12.591 --> 35:13.841
The magazines.

35:17.018 --> 35:19.107
Because they didn't bruise much.

35:21.790 --> 35:24.138
That's why I don't like being grabbed.

35:58.260 --> 35:59.268
- Okay.
- Okay.

35:59.299 --> 36:02.319
So you can tell anyone in here.

